15:43.342 --> 15:46.073
And let's not forget the mother
of all great sports stories --

15:46.145 --> 15:47.579
a double homicide
in Brentwood.

15:47.646 --> 15:49.444
If you want to talk,
I'm all for it.

15:49.515 --> 15:53.042
Really, I am. But let's talk about
