admire the bitter and the unemployed.

16:21.680 --> 16:23.409
-- <i>Are you mental?</i>
-- <i>I'll see you at airtime.</i>

16:23.482 --> 16:26.076
<i>Yeah, one thing you definitely don't
want to do is talk to your friends.</i>

16:26.151 --> 16:27.312
You know,
I wouldn't do that.

16:27.386 --> 16:29.047
Hey, I know you're pissed,
