16:33.592 --> 16:35.492
Danny, you're gonna find
another partner.

16:35.561 --> 16:37.529
Anybody would kill
to do this show with you.

16:37.596 --> 16:39.530
I've been here every day,
Casey --

16:39.598 --> 16:42.226
