for people like that.

16:59.451 --> 17:02.512
Now, the people here,
they like you --

17:02.588 --> 17:04.556
Isaac, Natalie,
Kim, Elliott.

17:04.623 --> 17:08.082
I don't know who this new guy, Jeremy,
is, but he seems to like you just fine.

17:08.160 --> 17:10.151
<i>Have you even noticed
that Dana's been keeping</i>

17:10.229 --> 17:12.993
J.J. and the network away from you
