17:13.065 --> 17:16.057
<i>Have you noticed that she's been
risking her job for you every day?</i>

17:16.135 --> 17:18.968
And do you really think, my friend, it
has that much to do with your talent?

17:19.038 --> 17:20.199
These are people
who like you, okay,

17:20.271 --> 17:22.502
-- Guys... -- and know what
you've been going through,

17:22.574 --> 17:25.839
-- and for three months now, you have shown us
nothing but the back of your hand, -- Guys...

17:25.911 --> 17:27.378
and now you're gonna show us
the door?

17:27.445 --> 17:29.073
Well, excuse me, all right,

17:29.148 --> 17:31.446
but the wisdom of your decision
isn't entirely clear to me here.

17:31.517 --> 17:33.007
-- Okay? Yeah, I'm pissed.
